Looking at this code, I can identify a critical bug in the "applet", "marquee", "object" end tag handling section:

```java
} else if (StringUtil.in(name, "applet", "marquee", "object")) {
    if (!tb.inScope("name")) {  // BUG: checking literal string "name" instead of variable name
